[Adapted from An Yimo's original novel,
The Charming Thief Princess]

41
00:02:01,610 --> 00:02:04,100
[Episode 21]

42
00:02:04,100 --> 00:02:05,970
[Eastern Palace]

43
00:02:18,260 --> 00:02:20,300
I've cursed him
for two days and two nights.

44
00:02:20,620 --> 00:02:23,060
That coward finally dares to see me?

45
00:02:25,700 --> 00:02:26,420
Douzi.

46
00:02:29,820 --> 00:02:31,380
Little Diviner.

47
00:02:31,740 --> 00:02:32,740
What are you doing here?

48
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:36,740
I heard you were locked up
in the Eastern Palace.

49
00:02:37,060 --> 00:02:38,060
I got worried,

50
00:02:38,260 --> 00:02:40,260
so I came to save you.

51
00:02:41,220 --> 00:02:42,140
Save me?

52
00:02:43,260 --> 00:02:44,580
What do you mean?

53
00:02:46,420 --> 00:02:47,220
Does

54
00:02:48,100 --> 00:02:50,740
Little Master... Does he know?

55
00:02:52,100 --> 00:02:54,620
The Crown Prince knows who you are.

56
00:02:54,740 --> 00:02:57,140
That's why he locked you up.

57
00:02:58,220 --> 00:02:59,340
Did he say anything?

58
00:02:59,340 --> 00:02:59,900
He...

59
00:03:01,780 --> 00:03:02,980
He didn't say anything.

60
00:03:03,900 --> 00:03:05,980
I don't know what he is thinking

61
00:03:06,220 --> 00:03:08,580
or what he plans to do to you.

62
00:03:11,020 --> 00:03:12,340
If he knows, he knows.

63
00:03:13,140 --> 00:03:17,060
We have to face it
sooner or later anyway.

64
00:03:18,940 --> 00:03:19,780
If you agree,

65
00:03:20,060 --> 00:03:22,580
I'll find a way to get you out of here.

66
00:03:23,180 --> 00:03:23,940
I'm not leaving.

67
00:03:24,660 --> 00:03:26,300
If he wants to arrest me,

68
00:03:26,420 --> 00:03:27,340
even if I'm out of here,

69
00:03:27,340 --> 00:03:28,460
he'll still bring me back.

70
00:03:28,460 --> 00:03:30,300
Although it's probably also dangerous
outside the palace,

71
00:03:30,740 --> 00:03:32,100
if you stay in the palace,

72
00:03:32,260 --> 00:03:33,460
your life will be in danger.

73
00:03:35,420 --> 00:03:36,500
For the Crown Prince,

74
00:03:36,620 --> 00:03:38,180
the bigger picture always comes first.

75
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:40,060
He can kill me if he wants to.

76
00:03:41,260 --> 00:03:43,660
I don't believe he could actually do it.

77
00:03:44,260 --> 00:03:47,100
It's probably because I cursed him
for two days and two nights,

78
00:03:47,100 --> 00:03:48,540
now he's too angry to see me.

79
00:03:49,820 --> 00:03:55,380
He said he'd cut his own head off,

80
00:03:55,540 --> 00:03:56,860
instead of hurting me.

81
00:03:57,900 --> 00:04:00,060
He has locked you up,

82
00:04:01,820 --> 00:04:03,340
yet you still trust him.

83
00:04:05,180 --> 00:04:06,700
I've tried so hard to protect you,

84
00:04:07,500 --> 00:04:08,900
but you choose to ignore it.

85
00:04:16,100 --> 00:04:17,460
You're so stubborn.

86
00:04:18,060 --> 00:04:19,540
Have you ever thought
about the consequences?

87
00:04:20,780 --> 00:04:22,100
If you stay in the palace,

88
00:04:22,460 --> 00:04:23,980
not only will you lose your life,

89
00:04:23,980 --> 00:04:25,180
the Crown Prince
will be implicated, too.

90
00:04:25,940 --> 00:04:28,860
Even the whole Jixi
will be destroyed because of you.

91
00:04:30,300 --> 00:04:31,500
Is this

92
00:04:33,060 --> 00:04:34,700
what you want?

93
00:04:38,060 --> 00:04:40,020
How could I have such strength
to make all this happen?

94
00:04:40,540 --> 00:04:42,180
Have you seen
the Little Master's ability?

95
00:04:43,180 --> 00:04:45,100
He can knock me out with a single punch.

96
00:04:45,580 --> 00:04:47,860
And I hate studying so much,

97
00:04:47,860 --> 00:04:49,660
yet I can't even destroy
the Chongwen Academy.

98
00:04:49,980 --> 00:04:51,260
How could I destroy a country?

99
00:04:52,180 --> 00:04:53,100
Besides,

100
00:04:53,820 --> 00:04:55,940
I never meant to hurt anyone.

101
00:04:56,740 --> 00:04:58,460
Even less likely to hurt Little Master.

102
00:05:03,300 --> 00:05:06,100
Do you think it's possible
that you had a bad dream one day

103
00:05:06,100 --> 00:05:07,180
and after you woke up,

104
00:05:07,180 --> 00:05:08,740
you blamed it on me?

105
00:05:09,540 --> 00:05:11,220
When the Crown Prince was still little,

106
00:05:11,420 --> 00:05:13,140
I predicted this.

107
00:05:13,660 --> 00:05:16,140
I had never even seen you back then.

108
00:05:25,260 --> 00:05:26,220
Douzi,

109
00:05:26,940 --> 00:05:27,860
trust me.

110
00:05:29,420 --> 00:05:32,580
As long as we can stay out of this...

111
00:05:34,740 --> 00:05:35,980
for the rest of my life,

112
00:05:36,860 --> 00:05:38,380
I promise to keep you safe.

113
00:05:41,740 --> 00:05:43,140
No matter what you say,

114
00:05:43,140 --> 00:05:44,340
I'm not leaving.

115
00:05:44,460 --> 00:05:45,420
You tell him to come to see me.

116
00:05:49,900 --> 00:05:52,140
You'd rather die with the Crown Prince

117
00:05:52,980 --> 00:05:54,780
than leave with me, right?

118
00:05:57,300 --> 00:05:58,460
You tell him to come to see me.

119
00:06:01,820 --> 00:06:03,180
You need to think this through.

120
00:06:04,620 --> 00:06:06,660
If this prophecy comes true,

121
00:06:08,540 --> 00:06:10,700
the two of you
won't be able to handle it.

122
00:06:27,140 --> 00:06:28,820
We've been friends for a while,

123
00:06:30,060 --> 00:06:31,180
yet it turns out

124
00:06:32,860 --> 00:06:34,660
that I am just an outsider to you.

125
00:06:47,020 --> 00:06:48,580
You are not

126
00:06:49,020 --> 00:06:50,580
supposed to be together.

127
00:06:51,060 --> 00:06:53,420
So don't blame me for breaking you up.

128
00:07:01,180 --> 00:07:06,820
Long live Your Highness.

129
00:07:09,420 --> 00:07:10,500
Please rise.

130
00:07:19,300 --> 00:07:19,860
Step aside.

131
00:07:24,100 --> 00:07:25,820
Mr. Bai, His Highness
is holding court.

132
00:07:29,380 --> 00:07:30,620
Who dares stop me?

133
00:07:44,100 --> 00:07:45,220
Bai Ye, what are you doing here?

134
00:07:45,460 --> 00:07:48,300
I'm here to inform everyone

135
00:07:49,260 --> 00:07:51,420
that I've found
the Princess of Shengdong

136
00:07:52,380 --> 00:07:53,620
who will destroy our country.

137
00:07:55,860 --> 00:07:56,980
Found her?

138
00:07:57,580 --> 00:07:58,380
Who is she?

139
00:07:58,380 --> 00:07:59,740
Bai Ye, have you lost your mind?

140
00:08:00,300 --> 00:08:01,980
You've found the Princess of Shengdong?

141
00:08:02,140 --> 00:08:02,980
Who is she?

142
00:08:03,100 --> 00:08:04,140
Where is she?

143
00:08:04,820 --> 00:08:06,620
She is the Grand Chancellor's daughter,

144
00:08:07,260 --> 00:08:08,780
Mei Yushan.

145
00:08:09,660 --> 00:08:10,460
Bai Ye!

146
00:08:11,300 --> 00:08:12,660
How could it be her?

147
00:08:12,660 --> 00:08:13,940
How could she be
the Grand Chancellor's daughter?

148
00:08:13,940 --> 00:08:15,220
That's nonsense.

149
00:08:15,460 --> 00:08:17,100
Bai Ye, how dare you!

150
00:08:17,260 --> 00:08:18,060
Your Highness,

151
00:08:18,540 --> 00:08:21,780
Mei Yushan is my own flesh and blood.

152
00:08:21,980 --> 00:08:23,740
How can she be
the Princess of Shengdong?

153
00:08:24,460 --> 00:08:26,900
Your Highness, I demand

154
00:08:26,980 --> 00:08:29,220
to expel him from the hall.

155
00:08:32,780 --> 00:08:35,460
The Mei Yushan I'm talking about
is not your daughter.

156
00:08:36,300 --> 00:08:37,860
Because of the Moon Spirit Pearl,

157
00:08:38,220 --> 00:08:41,460
Mei Yushan and the Princess of Shengdong
switched bodies.

158
00:08:42,540 --> 00:08:44,300
The Mei Yushan you see now

159
00:08:44,900 --> 00:08:46,500
is the Princess of Shengdong.

160
00:08:48,700 --> 00:08:51,620
And Mr. Mei, your own daughter

161
00:08:52,900 --> 00:08:55,500
has become her maid.

162
00:08:55,700 --> 00:08:57,180
This... This is impossible.

163
00:08:57,380 --> 00:08:59,460
Is there really such a ridiculous thing?

164
00:09:00,420 --> 00:09:01,500
Unbelievable.

165
00:09:06,580 --> 00:09:08,580
You shouldn't have shown up

166
00:09:10,380 --> 00:09:12,220
and said these words.

167
00:09:13,220 --> 00:09:14,340
Are you trying to get something?

168
00:09:17,620 --> 00:09:19,820
Or do you want to defy me in public?

169
00:09:22,060 --> 00:09:25,340
I'm just trying to protect you,
Your Highness,

170
00:09:25,500 --> 00:09:27,220
and the people of Jixi.

171
00:09:27,580 --> 00:09:29,100
Are you trying to protect me

172
00:09:29,580 --> 00:09:31,940
or getting revenge
for your unrequited love?

173
00:09:34,420 --> 00:09:36,060
You know better than them

174
00:09:36,060 --> 00:09:37,460
what the Crown Princess is like.

175
00:09:42,500 --> 00:09:43,380
I...

176
00:09:45,980 --> 00:09:47,780
don't believe she would hurt me.

177
00:09:48,980 --> 00:09:51,100
And I don't believe
she can destroy my country.

178
00:09:56,340 --> 00:09:57,020
Okay.

179
00:09:58,620 --> 00:09:59,940
Then I can tell you,

180
00:10:02,820 --> 00:10:04,420
I saw it with my own eyes.

181
00:10:05,340 --> 00:10:06,340
Your Highness...

182
00:10:09,020 --> 00:10:11,020
you will die by her hands.

183
00:10:15,580 --> 00:10:18,300
Bai Ye has never been wrong.

184
00:10:18,300 --> 00:10:20,020
Do you think she came here

185
00:10:20,180 --> 00:10:21,540
- to kill the Crown Prince?
- No way.

186
00:10:21,540 --> 00:10:22,540
Impossible.

187
00:10:22,940 --> 00:10:24,260
She can't even defeat me.

188
00:10:24,260 --> 00:10:25,740
So how can she kill His Highness?

189
00:10:25,740 --> 00:10:26,660
- The Crown Prince...
- Exactly.

190
00:10:26,660 --> 00:10:28,380
- is not seeing anyone.
- Right?

191
00:10:28,820 --> 00:10:30,340
I haven't seen
the Crown Prince in a while.

192
00:10:30,340 --> 00:10:31,140
Me neither.

193
00:10:31,140 --> 00:10:33,420
This girl has less manners,

194
00:10:34,780 --> 00:10:36,860
but it looks like
she will not harm others.

195
00:10:37,340 --> 00:10:38,740
I don't believe

196
00:10:39,860 --> 00:10:40,820
that she would kill His Highness.

197
00:10:41,420 --> 00:10:43,500
But Bai Ye has no grudge against her.

198
00:10:43,620 --> 00:10:44,980
- Why would he make this up...
- Yeah.

199
00:10:44,980 --> 00:10:46,140
to set her up?

200
00:10:48,260 --> 00:10:48,940
Pin,

201
00:10:49,540 --> 00:10:50,380
what do you think?

202
00:10:50,980 --> 00:10:52,060
Come here, all of you.

203
00:10:52,060 --> 00:10:53,100
Help me on this.

204
00:10:54,740 --> 00:10:56,740
With Pin's intelligence,
can he come up with anything brilliant?

205
00:10:57,740 --> 00:10:59,060
What are you drawing here?

206
00:10:59,380 --> 00:11:02,220
Mei Yushan is the Princess of Shengdong.

207
00:11:02,540 --> 00:11:04,180
Why would she kill His Highness?

208
00:11:04,460 --> 00:11:05,940
I told you her name wasn't Mei Yushan.

209
00:11:05,940 --> 00:11:07,100
It's weird.

210
00:11:07,260 --> 00:11:08,500
Her name is Douzi.

211
00:11:08,900 --> 00:11:09,820
How many times have I told you

212
00:11:09,820 --> 00:11:11,220
that they switched bodies?

213
00:11:12,620 --> 00:11:14,820
Mei and Douzi.

214
00:11:15,260 --> 00:11:15,980
I know now.

215
00:11:16,380 --> 00:11:18,460
Mei is the Princess of Shengdong.

216
00:11:19,820 --> 00:11:20,740
It's not like that.

217
00:11:20,740 --> 00:11:22,220
It's like you understood nothing.

218
00:11:22,460 --> 00:11:24,780
Her name is not Mei, but Douzi.

219
00:11:24,780 --> 00:11:27,260
Pin, there's no one called Mei.

220
00:11:27,420 --> 00:11:28,100
Right.

221
00:11:28,100 --> 00:11:29,860
You can't even figure
out such simple logic,

222
00:11:29,860 --> 00:11:30,940
yet you want to gossip with us.

223
00:11:32,140 --> 00:11:33,060
You're too stupid.

224
00:11:33,060 --> 00:11:34,620
I think we should ask Pin

225
00:11:34,620 --> 00:11:35,860
to deal with the Princess of Shengdong.

226
00:11:36,540 --> 00:11:37,460
Why?

227
00:11:38,420 --> 00:11:39,300
Because

228
00:11:39,740 --> 00:11:41,660
your stupidity can kill people.

229
00:11:42,980 --> 00:11:44,420
- Right.
- If you ask me,

230
00:11:44,540 --> 00:11:46,340
I'd say, fortunately,

231
00:11:46,340 --> 00:11:48,180
someone's going to give her a lesson.

232
00:11:48,620 --> 00:11:50,100
Do you remember the last time?

233
00:11:50,420 --> 00:11:52,780
She even cried for the rabbit
that we were going to hunt.

234
00:11:52,980 --> 00:11:55,020
Shengdong sent her
to kill the Crown Prince.

235
00:11:55,300 --> 00:11:56,900
Are all the people in her country dead?

236
00:11:56,900 --> 00:11:58,060
They are.

237
00:11:58,620 --> 00:12:00,660
My father fought in the war
to eliminate them.

238
00:12:00,660 --> 00:12:01,940
He was even awarded for it.

239
00:12:02,900 --> 00:12:04,020
She is indeed stupid.

240
00:12:04,020 --> 00:12:05,420
She's been taken down
before she becomes the Crown Princess.

241
00:12:05,420 --> 00:12:06,060
So stupid.

242
00:12:08,460 --> 00:12:09,900
With her little intelligence,

243
00:12:09,940 --> 00:12:11,140
her trying to destroy our country

244
00:12:11,660 --> 00:12:13,020
is a huge joke.

245
00:12:13,900 --> 00:12:14,740
Exactly.

246
00:12:15,020 --> 00:12:16,860
Yeah. She is not smart

247
00:12:16,860 --> 00:12:18,220
and she doesn't have
strong martial arts skills.

248
00:12:18,220 --> 00:12:19,980
The last time His Highness
taught her archery,

249
00:12:19,980 --> 00:12:22,100
she failed to master it after an hour.

250
00:12:22,300 --> 00:12:24,460
How could she kill someone?

251
00:12:26,980 --> 00:12:27,980
I think

252
00:12:28,340 --> 00:12:30,100
she is most likely wronged this time.

253
00:12:30,180 --> 00:12:31,500
What do we do then?

254
00:12:31,980 --> 00:12:33,900
Will Her Majesty kill her?

255
00:12:34,980 --> 00:12:38,020
Even though we don't usually like her,

256
00:12:38,420 --> 00:12:39,500
this time,

257
00:12:40,140 --> 00:12:41,260
we need to put that aside.

258
00:12:41,580 --> 00:12:42,140
It's...

259
00:12:42,220 --> 00:12:43,820
This time Douzi is in big trouble.

260
00:12:44,820 --> 00:12:45,780
Let's find a solution.

261
00:12:46,220 --> 00:12:47,380
Yeah, let's do something.

262
00:12:49,060 --> 00:12:51,460
[Eastern Palace]
The Princess of Shengdong is cunning.

263
00:12:51,500 --> 00:12:52,980
She's evil.

264
00:12:53,180 --> 00:12:57,260
Your Highness, we ask to see you,
and please don't be deceived by her.

265
00:12:57,660 --> 00:13:00,460
Your Highness, please make up your mind.

266
00:13:00,660 --> 00:13:02,100
Please make up your mind.

267
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:03,740
