00:26:35,740 --> 00:26:36,780
Treacherous ministers are in power.

545
00:26:38,620 --> 00:26:40,620
If we make him the Crown Prince,

546
00:26:41,780 --> 00:26:43,940
we'll be neglecting the Imperial Court
and our people,

547
00:26:45,780 --> 00:26:47,900
which is irresponsible and unfair.

548
00:26:52,060 --> 00:26:52,820
I, Nangong Yao,

549
00:26:52,820 --> 00:26:55,420
since childhood, have listened to Father
tell me how to be an emperor

550
00:26:56,500 --> 00:26:58,380
and the Grand Tutor tell me
how to govern the country.

551
00:27:00,940 --> 00:27:02,700
I can never do

552
00:27:05,700 --> 00:27:06,820
such irresponsible and unfair things.

553
00:27:07,140 --> 00:27:08,220
Well said.

554
00:27:08,580 --> 00:27:12,220
If your father hears this,

555
00:27:12,220 --> 00:27:14,140
he'll be incredibly gratified.

556
00:27:15,180 --> 00:27:16,100
Your Majesty.

557
00:27:16,540 --> 00:27:19,300
Your Majesty, you are wise.

558
00:27:19,540 --> 00:27:21,420
Considering my hard work

559
00:27:21,420 --> 00:27:22,940
over the years,

560
00:27:23,180 --> 00:27:24,820
please spare her life.

561
00:27:24,980 --> 00:27:27,620
It's... It's my daughter's body,
after all.

562
00:27:27,620 --> 00:27:28,740
Your Majesty.

563
00:27:28,740 --> 00:27:29,540
How dare you

564
00:27:30,660 --> 00:27:32,220
beg for mercy for the evil!

565
00:27:32,220 --> 00:27:33,260
Get him out of here.

566
00:27:34,420 --> 00:27:36,300
Your Majesty.

567
00:27:36,460 --> 00:27:39,380
Please spare her life, Your Majesty.

568
00:27:39,540 --> 00:27:41,340
Your Majesty...

569
00:27:59,140 --> 00:28:00,380
I've said before,

570
00:28:01,300 --> 00:28:03,060
that prophecy was nonsense.

571
00:28:04,460 --> 00:28:06,060
I can't believe the one
who will kill me in the end

572
00:28:07,220 --> 00:28:08,580
is you.

573
00:29:01,800 --> 00:29:02,820
[Tie the knot]

574
00:29:02,820 --> 00:29:04,180
The wedding is completed.

575
00:29:14,220 --> 00:29:16,180
Best wishes to the Crown Prince
and the Crown Princess.

576
00:29:16,380 --> 00:29:17,580
We wish you a happy marriage

577
00:29:17,780 --> 00:29:19,020
for a hundred years.

578
00:29:19,340 --> 00:29:20,740
You are destined for one another

579
00:29:20,940 --> 00:29:22,940
and will grow old together.

580
00:29:22,940 --> 00:29:24,220
Ridiculous.

581
00:29:25,100 --> 00:29:26,900
The Crown Prince is stupid.

582
00:29:28,140 --> 00:29:30,540
This... This is not proper.

583
00:29:31,060 --> 00:29:33,260
How could you do such a reckless thing?

584
00:29:36,740 --> 00:29:37,660
I told you,

585
00:29:40,060 --> 00:29:41,820
I'd rather cut off my own head

586
00:29:44,620 --> 00:29:46,540
than hurt you.

587
00:29:52,340 --> 00:29:53,380
Abdicate.

588
00:29:53,980 --> 00:29:54,900
Abdicate.

589
00:29:58,540 --> 00:30:00,020
I am the master of my fate.

590
00:30:09,060 --> 00:30:10,620
I will make her the Crown Princess,
which cannot be changed.

591
00:30:12,180 --> 00:30:13,300
I want both the country

592
00:30:15,020 --> 00:30:15,980
and my lover.

593
00:30:17,300 --> 00:30:19,540
Lock this evil girl up.

594
00:30:24,180 --> 00:30:25,660
Let me out.

595
00:30:25,700 --> 00:30:27,940
Who are you to lock me up?

596
00:30:27,940 --> 00:30:29,620
I didn't kill or rob anyone.

597
00:30:29,620 --> 00:30:31,060
It's those eunuchs

598
00:30:31,100 --> 00:30:32,940
who work for the Empress.

599
00:30:32,940 --> 00:30:34,940
Come out and take me on.

600
00:30:34,940 --> 00:30:35,820
Stop yelling.

601
00:30:35,860 --> 00:30:37,020
- You stupid ministers.
- The whole palace

602
00:30:37,020 --> 00:30:38,220
is full of your voice.

603
00:30:39,660 --> 00:30:41,380
Eat a steamed bun and shut up.

604
00:30:42,620 --> 00:30:43,740
Are there more steamed buns?

605
00:30:43,740 --> 00:30:44,660
And get me some water.

606
00:30:44,660 --> 00:30:45,980
I got so thirsty after scolding
for a long time.

607
00:30:46,980 --> 00:30:48,460
It's not like
they'll cut your head off tomorrow.

608
00:30:48,460 --> 00:30:49,660
Do you have to eat that much?

609
00:30:49,740 --> 00:30:50,980
Only when I'm full,
do I have the strength

610
00:30:51,020 --> 00:30:51,780
to keep yelling at you.

611
00:30:51,780 --> 00:30:53,300
Okay, okay. I'll get them for you.

612
00:30:54,700 --> 00:30:57,220
Keeping her here for two more days,
we'll be poor.

613
00:30:58,220 --> 00:31:01,060
She isn't going to destroy
our country like this, is she?

614
00:31:10,980 --> 00:31:11,620
Let's go.

615
00:31:14,540 --> 00:31:15,180
Hurry.

616
00:31:19,540 --> 00:31:20,300
Here she is.

617
00:31:23,500 --> 00:31:24,060
Hey.

618
00:31:27,340 --> 00:31:28,100
What?

619
00:31:28,260 --> 00:31:29,420
You came to laugh at me?

620
00:31:29,820 --> 00:31:30,980
I need to warn you,

621
00:31:31,220 --> 00:31:33,380
I have just built up my strength

622
00:31:33,540 --> 00:31:35,460
and tried to find someone to scold now.

623
00:31:36,500 --> 00:31:37,180
Look.

624
00:31:37,340 --> 00:31:39,860
The prison meals
we have in Jixi are nutritious.

625
00:31:40,420 --> 00:31:41,820
Not only did she not lose weight

626
00:31:41,940 --> 00:31:43,260
but also gained some.

627
00:31:44,660 --> 00:31:45,900
So what if I gained some weight?

628
00:31:45,980 --> 00:31:47,620
I can stand steadily.

629
00:31:47,700 --> 00:31:49,380
Not like you

630
00:31:49,380 --> 00:31:50,980
who will be blown away by the wind.

631
00:31:51,100 --> 00:31:52,260
When Zhuang Yanyang holds you,

632
00:31:52,260 --> 00:31:53,900
it's like she's holding a big kite.

633
00:31:53,900 --> 00:31:54,460
You...

634
00:31:55,660 --> 00:31:57,060
Look at how she talks.

635
00:31:57,060 --> 00:31:59,100
It seems she hasn't suffered much.

636
00:32:00,260 --> 00:32:00,780
Come on.

637
00:32:01,340 --> 00:32:03,220
If you guys want to laugh at me,
just come alone.

638
00:32:03,220 --> 00:32:05,180
Why do you call everyone else here?

639
00:32:05,180 --> 00:32:06,100
You are right.

640
00:32:06,140 --> 00:32:07,420
We skipped class

641
00:32:07,420 --> 00:32:08,860
just to make fun of you.

642
00:32:09,620 --> 00:32:10,780
That's right.

643
00:32:10,780 --> 00:32:12,580
You need to stand steadily.

644
00:32:12,660 --> 00:32:14,260
So everyone can see

645
00:32:14,260 --> 00:32:16,300
there's no difference

646
00:32:16,300 --> 00:32:17,540
between you and us.

647
00:32:17,540 --> 00:32:18,540
You don't look like an evil girl at all.

648
00:32:18,540 --> 00:32:19,620
They're teasing you.

649
00:32:19,620 --> 00:32:21,540
We are all here to visit you.

650
00:32:21,980 --> 00:32:24,380
With your intelligence,
you and Pin can be a good match.

651
00:32:25,300 --> 00:32:27,420
If you can't be the Crown Princess,

652
00:32:27,540 --> 00:32:30,180
it's not bad to be the Eighth Princess.

653
00:32:30,740 --> 00:32:31,700
Who are you talking about?

654
00:32:34,940 --> 00:32:37,380
This rose gel is for your face.

655
00:32:37,540 --> 00:32:39,260
Bad air here will make you age faster.

656
00:32:39,820 --> 00:32:40,700
Thank you.

657
00:32:40,860 --> 00:32:42,220
It's not that I feel bad for you.

658
00:32:42,460 --> 00:32:44,980
I'm afraid if the Crown Princess
is someone old and ugly,

659
00:32:44,980 --> 00:32:46,420
it'll be a shame
on our Chongwen Academy.

660
00:32:48,020 --> 00:32:50,100
I bring you stinky tofu.

661
00:32:52,580 --> 00:32:53,780
Just take it.

662
00:32:53,780 --> 00:32:54,780
It stinks.

663
00:32:56,540 --> 00:32:57,340
Thank you.

664
00:32:58,740 --> 00:33:00,460
I was going to teach you a few moves

665
00:33:00,460 --> 00:33:01,940
to take down the guards.

666
00:33:02,340 --> 00:33:03,980
But it's too narrow here.

667
00:33:03,980 --> 00:33:05,260
I can't move.

668
00:33:05,340 --> 00:33:07,060
It's okay. I appreciate it.

669
00:33:07,540 --> 00:33:09,060
What do you bring, Pin?

670
00:33:09,180 --> 00:33:09,940
Me?

671
00:33:10,900 --> 00:33:12,140
I have a question.

672
00:33:12,620 --> 00:33:13,860
What question?

673
00:33:14,340 --> 00:33:16,540
So are you Douzi or Mei?

674
00:33:18,260 --> 00:33:19,540
Everyone.

675
00:33:19,540 --> 00:33:20,780
We need to keep our voices down.

676
00:33:20,780 --> 00:33:22,660
We're here for a secret prison visit.

677
00:33:22,780 --> 00:33:24,060
It's not entertainment.

678
00:33:24,220 --> 00:33:26,020
Yeah, yeah. Let's get out of here.

679
00:33:26,020 --> 00:33:27,500
If they find out, we will be doomed.

680
00:33:27,740 --> 00:33:28,500
Let's go.

681
00:33:28,500 --> 00:33:31,140
Wait, you're already leaving?

682
00:33:32,860 --> 00:33:34,340
Take good care of yourself.

683
00:33:34,940 --> 00:33:36,380
We'll visit you another time.

684
00:33:36,580 --> 00:33:37,060
Yes.

685
00:33:37,060 --> 00:33:38,420
- Take care of yourself.
- Bye.

686
00:33:38,540 --> 00:33:39,140
Let's go. Let's go.

687
00:33:39,140 --> 00:33:39,740
Let's go.

688
00:34:18,900 --> 00:34:19,500
Sorry, I made you suffer.

689
00:34:19,500 --> 00:34:21,420
I miss you.

690
00:34:24,380 --> 00:34:26,140
I miss you so much.

691
00:34:30,700 --> 00:34:31,460
Me too.

692
00:34:32,460 --> 00:34:33,820
I miss you day and night.

693
00:34:35,940 --> 00:34:37,420
Locking me up in the Eastern Palace
for so long,

694
00:34:37,420 --> 00:34:38,620
you hadn't come to see me.

695
00:34:38,620 --> 00:34:39,860
When you finally came,

696
00:34:39,860 --> 00:34:41,820
you spoke so ruthlessly.

697
00:34:42,220 --> 00:34:43,540
Today in the hall,

698
00:34:43,660 --> 00:34:45,500
I really thought
you were going to kill me.

699
00:34:45,500 --> 00:34:47,060
My heart was broken.

700
00:34:49,460 --> 00:34:50,500
It's my fault.

701
00:34:51,140 --> 00:34:52,740
It will never happen again.

702
00:34:53,180 --> 00:34:57,620
So what you said
in the hall still stands?

703
00:34:58,660 --> 00:34:59,660
What was it again?

704
00:35:00,180 --> 00:35:01,580
Getting married!

705
00:35:01,580 --> 00:35:02,780
Forget it.

706
00:35:05,460 --> 00:35:06,620
Of course, it stands.

707
00:35:06,860 --> 00:35:07,700
Silly girl.

708
00:35:13,500 --> 00:35:17,620
But I worry about that prophecy.

709
00:35:18,300 --> 00:35:19,540
Don't you?

710
00:35:19,980 --> 00:35:21,140
That hasn't happened yet.

711
00:35:21,380 --> 00:35:22,340
We don't need to worry about it.

712
00:35:23,060 --> 00:35:25,140
Let me take care of what's going on now.

713
00:35:27,060 --> 00:35:30,180
Now you believe
that I won't hurt you, right?

714
00:35:31,660 --> 00:35:32,420
Of course.

715
00:35:33,500 --> 00:35:35,660
Yesterday when the ministers came
to the Eastern Palace to make trouble,

716
00:35:36,140 --> 00:35:37,340
Dongxi left the palace

717
00:35:37,340 --> 00:35:39,340
and did a background check
on you and your three fathers.

718
00:35:40,060 --> 00:35:40,820
He is sure

719
00:35:41,740 --> 00:35:43,100
that you didn't know who you were.

720
00:35:43,100 --> 00:35:44,980
Did you send Dongxi to do so?

721
00:35:45,460 --> 00:35:46,300
Of course, not.

722
00:35:46,940 --> 00:35:47,980
Even if he didn't check,

723
00:35:49,340 --> 00:35:50,380
I'll still believe you.

724
00:35:51,100 --> 00:35:51,740
Besides,

725
00:35:53,420 --> 00:35:54,580
I never doubted you.

726
00:35:55,900 --> 00:35:57,860
I'm full of energy right now.

727
00:35:58,060 --> 00:35:59,820
I just ate eight steamed buns.

728
00:36:00,220 --> 00:36:02,820
I think I can still fight those monsters

729
00:36:02,820 --> 00:36:04,260
for a few days.

730
00:36:05,620 --> 00:36:06,540
I can't believe

731
00:36:06,540 --> 00:36:07,460
you can still eat now.

732
00:36:08,620 --> 00:36:10,660
Don't worry. You won't have to.

733
00:36:10,940 --> 00:36:12,500
Just let me protect you.

734
00:36:14,900 --> 00:36:17,540
By the way,
it's chaotic in the palace now.

735
00:36:17,660 --> 00:36:19,620
I'd like to get you out
as soon as possible.

736
00:36:20,220 --> 00:36:22,180
I'll pick you up
after I take care of everything.

737
00:36:25,660 --> 00:36:28,380
I can still leave the palace now?

738
00:36:29,980 --> 00:36:31,020
I'll arrange it secretly

739
00:36:31,260 --> 00:36:32,420
by weakening the palace's defense

740
00:36:32,420 --> 00:36:33,460
and getting you out of the palace.

741
00:36:34,540 --> 00:36:35,380
Better sooner than later.

742
00:36:36,100 --> 00:36:37,260
If everything goes well,

743
00:36:37,460 --> 00:36:38,660
you can leave tomorrow night.

744
00:36:41,420 --> 00:36:42,780
I can't stay here too long.

745
00:36:43,380 --> 00:36:44,380
It'll cause suspicion.

746
00:36:45,100 --> 00:36:47,260
Well... Then you better go.

747
00:36:54,740 --> 00:36:55,940
Your clothes are dirty.

748
00:36:57,420 --> 00:36:58,180
No.

749
00:36:58,340 --> 00:36:59,460
I was wrong.

750
00:37:03,660 --> 00:37:04,980
Let me straighten your clothes for you.

751
00:37:25,340 --> 00:37:26,180
Done.

752
00:37:26,620 --> 00:37:27,300
You may go now.

753
00:37:31,220 --> 00:37:32,140
You don't want me to leave?

754
00:37:33,820 --> 00:37:35,660
You didn't leave?

755
00:37:54,660 --> 00:37:55,420
Be good.

756
00:37:56,300 --> 00:37:57,540
After I take care of everything,

757
00:37:57,660 --> 00:37:58,580
I'll come back for you.

758
00:37:59,780 --> 00:38:02,140
Look at the moon when you miss me.

759
00:38:02,540 --> 00:38:05,470
♪It's your mesmerizing glance♪

760
